Available Tools: get_temperature | get_humidity | get_wind_speed | get_uv_index
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "location": "string", "unit": "celsius|fahrenheit" }
Response Schema: { "value": number, "unit": "string", "timestamp": "string" }
---
Question: What is the UV index currently in Austin?
Call: { "func_call": "get_uv_index", "location": "Austin", "unit": "celsius" }
Response: { "value": 9.2, "unit": "index", "timestamp": "2023-10-28T09:15:00Z" }

Question: Check the temperature in Boston right now.
Call: { "func_call": "get_temperature", "location": "Boston", "unit": "fahrenheit" }
Response: { "value": 54.3, "unit": "°F", "timestamp": "2023-10-28T09:16:00Z" }

